# 🧠 CoachWise – Your AI Career Coach

CoachWise is a full-stack, AI-powered career coaching platform designed to help individuals build stronger resumes, generate personalized career roadmaps, and get expert-level guidance for professional growth — all in one place.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ **AI Resume Analyzer** – Upload your resume and get instant, intelligent feedback powered by LLMs.
- 💬 **Career Q&A Chatbot** – Ask job-related questions and get real-time answers using Gemini AI.
- 🗺️ **Career Roadmap Generator** – Receive skill-based, role-specific roadmaps for your dream job.
- 📝 **Cover Letter Generator** *(coming soon)* – Auto-generate tailored cover letters based on your resume and job description.
- 🔐 **Secure Auth** – Authentication via Clerk with Google/email login.
- 💳 **Billing System** – Stripe integration for subscription-based access.
- 🧠 **Background Jobs** – Powered by Inngest for resume parsing, AI processing, and async tasks.
- 📄 **PDF Preview** – Beautiful PDF viewer to show uploaded resumes and AI feedback side-by-side.

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Layer           | Tech Used |
|------------------|-----------|
| **Frontend**     | Next.js 15, Tailwind CSS, ShadCN UI, Framer Motion |
| **Authentication** | Clerk |
| **Billing**       | Stripe |
| **AI & LLM**      | Gemini API (via axios), LangChain |
| **Background Jobs** | Inngest |
| **Database**      | Neon (PostgreSQL), Drizzle ORM |
| **UI Tools**      | Radix UI, Lucide Icons, Sonner Toasts |
| **Roadmap Visualization** | @xyflow/react (React Flow) |

